Have Fun on the Toilet

Gosh! I really need a pee!
"Have fun!", is what they said to me.
Sure I'll dance a wee jig
And sing a little song
For pishing on the toilet
Is always a game to me.
Sometimes I pee sitting down
And sometimes I stand on my hands
Just to see the water flow
And splish splash into the loo.
Well there's a secret you see
That when I do a pee
